```
./app/globals.css:1726:12
Parsing CSS source code failed
  1724 | }
  1725 | .gap-\[--spacing\(var\(--gap\)\)\] {
> 1726 |   gap: var(--spacing(var(--gap)));
       |            ^
  1727 | }

Unexpected token Function("--spacing")
```

The issue is in `app/globals.css` at line 1726. The CSS value `var(--spacing(var(--gap)))` is invalid CSS - you can't nest function calls like that in CSS.

